  "_source": "Captured from a real architect-LLM run (deepseek-v4-pro) on the prompt 'multi-tenant SaaS for small gyms to manage members, class schedules, and bookings' (2026-06-26). This exact shape broke the generator four ways before the fixes — explicit `id` fields, `table.column` FK refs, indirect ownership via a user_id FK, and an `auth.users.id` self-link. Kept as a regression fixture so the corpus grows from REAL model output, not author-imagined shapes.",
